Function get-Unixdate ($UnixDate) {
    [timezone]::CurrentTimeZone.ToLocalTime(([datetime]'1/1/1970').AddSeconds($UnixDate)) 
}

 


Remove-Item \\gremlin\d$\BKD_LOGS\Duplication\VerifyOn_Offsite\AllImagesDUser.txt
Remove-Item \\gremlin\d$\BKD_LOGS\Duplication\VerifyOn_Offsite\ImagelistDUser.txt
